Here is the world,

48
00:01:51,450 --> 00:01:53,910
and we have a lot of edge locations around the world.

49
00:01:53,910 --> 00:01:57,480
Now, the Price Class 100 is going to give us the America,

50
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,460
the North America, and Europe,

51
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:02,880
then Price Class 200 is going to add some of these regions,

52
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:04,320
and Price Class All

53
00:02:04,320 --> 00:02:07,410
is going to have the entire world available

54
00:02:07,410 --> 00:02:10,259
for the edge locations.

